OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRadio DJ Chris Evans       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freveals skin cancer        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdiagnosis                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, DJ Chris Evans has revealed he has been
OL,6, diagnosed with skin cancer.            
OL,8,FThe 57-year-old announced the news on  
OL,9,Fhis Virgin Radio show on Monday, urging
OL,10,Fothers to get themselves checked.      
OL,12,FHe told listeners he was tested for the
OL,13,Fdisease after his "angel" of a masseur 
OL,14,Ffound "a mark" on his shin and that it 
OL,15,Fhad been "caught as early as possible".
OL,17,FIt comes eight years after the former  
OL,18,FBBC Radio 1 and Radio 2 broadcaster was
OL,19,Fgiven the all-clear following a        
OL,20,Fprostate cancer scare.                 
